<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٥٣٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4670">عُمَرُ بْنُ حَفْصٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1556">أَبِي </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشُ: </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">شَقِيقٌ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدَ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«أَوَّلُ مَا يُقْضَى بَيْنَ النَّاسِ بِالدِّمَاءِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>